Global E-House Market Insights
E-House Market size was valued at USD 4.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.7% from 2024 to 2030.

E-House Market Overview
The E-House market has seen significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for automated and intelligent solutions in energy management and infrastructure. As industries across the globe focus on improving operational efficiency, the E-House market is projected to grow at a substantial rate. The market value of the E-House is estimated to reach USD 9.7 billion by 2028, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2021 to 2028. Key industries such as power generation, mining, and oil & gas are increasingly adopting E-Houses for their efficiency, safety, and scalability. The expansion of renewable energy projects is also fueling the demand for such solutions.

